{Nightshade}

    A swift and silent shadow darted across the landscape mirroring the bird
bots path, her beast form ran silently as she bound behind and to the far
left of Sunhawk. In the confusion of the general melee she had taken the
opportunity to position herself apart from both groups to follow the maximal
in the inevitable retreat he had to make.

    Some cards had to be thrown on the table if the bot was the example of
the maximals that were on their trail. Smiling a foxy grin she quickened her
pace to make sure she didn't lose the flyer. She was careful to keep her
signature masked so he couldn't detect her with sensors, unless he turned
and actively searched the ground she doubted he'd notice her.
